- add the ability to highlight patterns
- need to trim the HTML content in "output" once it is past a certain length
- make silencing RT messages when one or more scripts is running the default,
  but keep it configurable.
- add the ability to re-{calculate,configure} screen cols/rows
- move "htmlify" to the server-side (add it as a string refinement) -- control
  whether or not it is invoked by a config-flag (rip out "jquery-reduce.js" upon
  completion)
- add "to_snake_case" string refinement (accept opts, e.g. "symbolize" default:
  false)
- add "to_camel_case" string refinement (accept opts, e.g. "lower" default:
  false)
- add "snake_case_keys" hash refinement (accept opts, e.g. "symbolize" default:
  false)
- add "camel_case_keys" hash refinement (accept opts, e.g. "symbolize" default:
  false, "lower" default: false)

